{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896101573,"sessionID":"ses_28458bfd8ffebRFWZ5Yu42e54k","part":{"id":"prt_d7ba8029600173Lwrip7J8j86k","messageID":"msg_d7ba7ecc6001hSLcuy99C06u5z","sessionID":"ses_28458bfd8ffebRFWZ5Yu42e54k","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-f340017cd8104c93b6a3c3f6ca841021","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/deployment/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # pkg/apis — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition Design\n2: \n3: ## AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n4: \n5: **Module**: `pkg/apis`  \n6: **Language**: Go  \n7: **Size**: S  \n8: **Purpose**: Define Kubernetes CRDs for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources, enable client-go generation, and provide type-safe API access.\n9: \n10: ## Architecture\n11: \n12: ### Package Structure\n13: \n14: ```\n15: pkg/apis/\n16: ├── runtime/\n17: │   └── v1alpha1/\n18: │       ├── agentruntime_types.go   # AgentRuntime spec/status\n19: │       ├── codeinterpreter_types.go # CodeInterpreter spec/status\n20: │       ├── doc.go                   # Package documentation\n21: │       ├── groupversion_info.go     # GroupVersion constants\n22: │       ├── register.go              # Scheme registration\n23: │       └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go # DeepCopy methods (controller-gen)\n24: client-go/                          # Generated client library\n25: └── runtime/\n26:     └── v1alpha1/                   # Generated types (symlink or copy)\n27: ```\n28: \n29: ### API Group\n30: \n31: - **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n32: - **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n33: - **Scope**: `Namespaced`\n34: \n35: ### Component Interactions\n36: \n37: ```\n38: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n39: │                    Kubernetes API Server                │\n40: │                                                          │\n41: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n42: │  │         runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1    │  │\n43: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n44: │  │  │  agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh │  │  │\n45: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n46: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n47: │  │  │  codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh││  │\n48: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n49: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n50: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n51:                           │\n52:                           │ k8s client-go\n53:                           ▼\n54: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n55: │                 client-go (Generated)                   │\n56: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n57: │  │  clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/     │  │\n58: │  │    • AgentRuntimeInterface                       │  │\n59: │  │    • CodeInterpreterInterface                    │  │\n60: │  │    • REST CRUD + Watch                           │  │\n61: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n62: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n63: │  │  informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/    │  │\n64: │  │    • AgentRuntimeInformer                        │  │\n65: │  │    • CodeInterpreterInformer                     │  │\n66: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n67: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n68: │  │  listers/runtime/v1alpha1/                      │  │\n69: │  │    • AgentRuntimeLister                          │  │\n70: │  │    • CodeInterpreterLister                       │  │\n71: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n72: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n73: ```\n74: \n75: ## Data Structures\n76: \n77: ### AgentRuntime\n78: \n79: **File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n80: \n81: ```go\n82: // AgentRuntimeSpec defines the desired state of AgentRuntime\n83: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n84:     // MaxSessionDuration is the maximum duration for any session\n85:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n86:     MaxSessionDuration string `json:\"maxSessionDuration\"`\n87:     \n88:     // SessionTimeout is the idle timeout before a session is terminated\n89:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n90:     SessionTimeout string `json:\"sessionTimeout\"`\n91:     \n92:     // TargetPort specifies the HTTP/HTTPS ports to expose\n93:     // +kubebuilder:validation:MinItems=1\n94:     TargetPort []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n95:     \n96:     // PodTemplate defines the pod template for agent sandbox pods\n97:     PodTemplate PodTemplateSpec `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n98: }\n99: \n100: // AgentRuntimeStatus defines the observed state of AgentRuntime\n101: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n102:     // Conditions represent the latest available observations\n103:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n104:     \n105:     // ObservedGeneration is the most recent generation observed\n106:     ObservedGeneration int64 `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"`\n107: }\n108: \n109: // TargetPort defines a single HTTP/HTTPS port target\n110: type TargetPort struct {\n111:     // Port is the port number\n112:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=1\n113:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Maximum=65535\n114:     Port int32 `json:\"port\"`\n115:     \n116:     // Protocol must be \"HTTP\" or \"HTTPS\"\n117:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n118:     Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n119:     \n120:     // Name is an optional name for the port\n121:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n122:     \n123:     // PathPrefix is the URL path prefix for this port\n124:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n125: }\n126: \n127: // PodTemplateSpec defines the pod template specification\n128: type PodTemplateSpec struct {\n129:     // Metadata for the pod\n130:     Metadata metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n131:     \n132:     // Spec for the pod\n133:     Spec PodSpec `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n134: }\n135: \n136: // AgentRuntime is the Schema for the agentruntimes API\n137: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n138: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n139: // +kubebuilder:resource:shortName=art\n140: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n141: type AgentRuntime struct {\n142:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n143:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n144:     \n145:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n146:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n147: }\n148: \n149: // AgentRuntimeList contains a list of AgentRuntime\n150: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n151: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n152:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n153:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n154:     \n155:     Items []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n156: }\n157: ```\n158: \n159: ### CodeInterpreter\n160: \n161: **File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n162: \n163: ```go\n164: // CodeInterpreterSpec defines the desired state of CodeInterpreter\n165: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n166:     // AuthMode specifies the authentication mode\n167:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n168:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n169:     AuthMode string `json:\"authMode\"`\n170:     \n171:     // MaxSessionDuration is the maximum duration for any session\n172:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n173:     MaxSessionDuration string `json:\"maxSessionDuration\"`\n174:     \n175:     // SessionTimeout is the idle ti